goal, research }`, where `research` is a JSON-stringifiable object\nwith `topic`, `executive_summary`, `findings`, `conclusion`, and `sources`. Ground its findings only\nin the supplied document text and `specialistFacts`; sources must be empty because supplied material\nis not web research. Emit ONE `currentTask.resolve({ scopes: [...] })` statement.","structuredPatch":[{"oldStart":4,"oldLines":6,"newStart":4,"newLines":8,"lines":["   scopes: array"," role: explore"," functions: []","+prelude: |","+  const documents = await Promise.all((attachmentIds as string[]).map((id) => readDocument(id)));"," ---"," "," Identify the coarsest complete partition of independently owned scopes in the supplied material."]}],"userModified":false,"replaceAll":false}}
